&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif;&quot;&gt;This role is ideal for a chef who thrives in dynamic environments and enjoys working closely with customers through in-person kitchen visits, product demonstrations, and menu innovation sessions. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif;&quot;&gt;The Corporate Chef will collaborate cross-functionally with Sales, Marketing, Innovation, and Supply Chain teams, reporting directly to the Head of Culinary.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Travel Requirement&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
